@startuml fig6_designreq
!theme plain
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam StateBackgroundColor #F5F8FC
skinparam StateBorderColor #1F4E79

[*] --> New : Customer creates request

New --> InReview : Sales (+1 step)
InReview --> Quoted : Sales (+1 step)
Quoted --> Done : Sales (+1 step)
Done --> [*]

note right of New
  Exactly one step at a time.
  Skipping (New to Done) is rejected.
end note
@enduml
